Class JavaScriptObjectDecorator

java.lang.Object
  com.totsp.gwittir.client.jsni.JavaScriptObjectDecorator

public class JavaScriptObjectDecorator
extends java.lang.Object

This is a wrapper class around JavaScriptObject that allows for quick access to data values on the JSO.
